Don't touch me!", whilst shocked police officers are seen fighting to arrest unruly migrants. More than 2,000 (!) sexual assaults and robberies as well as numerous (no accurate numbers have been published) rapes were reported, mainly in Cologne city centre. Similar incidents were also reported throughout Germany, including Hamburg, Frankfurt, Dortmund, Düsseldorf, Stuttgart, and Bielefeld.
